00:01:00.370 --> 00:01:03.560
The foundation underwrites
important work relating

00:01:03.560 --> 00:01:06.410
to caricature and cartoon
here at the library,

00:01:06.410 --> 00:01:09.860
and this includes
preservation and processing

00:01:09.860 --> 00:01:12.530
of the library's
holdings of comic art,

00:01:12.530 --> 00:01:14.070
development of these
collections,

00:01:14.070 --> 00:01:17.450
